<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <style>
        * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

        body {
            font-family: 'Georgia', serif;
            background: #fff;
            color: #333;
        }

        .certificate {
            width: 100%;
            min-height: 100vh;
            padding: 40px;
            border: 12px solid #2c3e50;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            position: relative;
            background: #fff;
        }

        .certificate::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 20px; left: 20px; right: 20px; bottom: 20px;
            border: 3px solid #c9a84c;
        }

        .header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        .header .logo-text {
            font-size: 13px;
            color: #888;
            letter-spacing: 4px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .header h1 {
            font-size: 42px;
            color: #2c3e50;
            font-weight: bold;
            letter-spacing: 3px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #c9a84c;
            padding-bottom: 15px;
            display: inline-block;
        }

        .subtitle {
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #777;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }

        .presented-to {
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 13px;
            color: #555;
            margin: 20px 0 5px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
        }

        .recipient-name {
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 38px;
            color: #c9a84c;
            font-style: italic;
            margin: 10px 0 25px;
            font-family: 'Georgia', serif;
        }

        .body-text {
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #555;
            line-height: 1.8;
            margin: 15px auto;
            max-width: 600px;
        }

        .formation-name {
            font-size: 22px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #2c3e50;
            text-align: center;
            margin: 15px 0;
            padding: 10px 30px;
            border-top: 1px solid #c9a84c;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #c9a84c;
            display: inline-block;
        }

        .formation-wrap {
            text-align: center;
            margin: 10px 0 20px;
        }

        .score-section {
            text-align: center;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }

        .score-badge {
            display: inline-block;
            background: #2c3e50;
            color: #c9a84c;
            font-size: 20px;
            font-weight: bold;
            padding: 10px 30px;
            border-radius: 4px;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
        }

        .badge-label {
            display: inline-block;
            margin-left: 10px;
            background: #c9a84c;
            color: #fff;
            font-size: 14px;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border-radius: 4px;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }

        .footer {
            margin-top: 50px;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: flex-end;
            padding: 0 40px;
        }

        .sign-block {
            text-align: center;
        }

        .sign-line {
            width: 180px;
            border-top: 1px solid #333;
            margin: 0 auto 5px;
        }

        .sign-label {
            font-size: 11px;
            color: #888;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
        }

        .date-block {
            text-align: center;
        }

        .seal {
            width: 80px;
            height: 80px;
            border: 3px solid #c9a84c;
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            margin: 0 auto;
            color: #c9a84c;
            font-size: 11px;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
            text-align: center;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="certificate">

    <div class="header">
        <p class="logo-text">Plateforme de Formation Professionnelle</p>
        <h1>Certificat de Réussite</h1>
    </div>

    <p class="subtitle">Ce certificat est décerné à</p>

    <p class="recipient-name">{{ participantName }}</p>

    <p class="body-text">
        Pour avoir complété avec succès la formation et réussi l'évaluation associée
        avec un résultat satisfaisant.
    </p>

    <div class="formation-wrap">
        <span class="formation-name">{{ formation.nomForm }}</span>
    </div>

    <p class="body-text">
        Type : <strong>{{ formation.type }}</strong> &nbsp;|&nbsp;
        Date : <strong>{{ formation.dateForm ? formation.dateForm|date('d/m/Y') : 'N/A' }}</strong>
    </p>

    <div class="score-section">
        <span class="score-badge">Score : {{ score }} / {{ total }}</span>
        <span class="badge-label">{{ badge }}</span>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
        <div class="sign-block">
            <div class="sign-line"></div>
            <p class="sign-label">Directeur de Formation</p>
        </div>

        <div class="seal">
            OFFICIEL
        </div>

        <div class="date-block">
            <div class="sign-line"></div>
            <p class="sign-label">Date : {{ "now"|date("d/m/Y") }}</p>
        </div>
    </div>

</div>
</body>
</html>